      Types of work we support
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-12">

      <!-- Block 1: Design and documentation support -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4">Design and documentation support</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          MTL Partners provides ongoing design and documentation work for partner organizations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
          This includes proposals, layouts, and structured materials used in day-to-day operations.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Block 2: System management and technical operations -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-white mb-4">System management and technical operations</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          We maintain and support systems used by partner organizations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-3">
          This includes managing workflows, organizing information, and ensuring systems remain consistent and usable over time.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
